            <span>Specialist in self-employed marine professional &amp; small-practice mortgages</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="hero-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3787839/pexels-photo-3787839.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Yacht surveyor inspecting a hull at the marina" width="1200" height="1500" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1200x1500/0A0E1A/E8EEFF/png?text=Yacht+Surveyor';">
