    <div class="container">
      <div class="final-cta-inner">
        <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Talk to a yacht-surveyor mortgage specialist</div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--paper);">Get a yacht surveyor mortgage from a lender who reads Schedule C.</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(250,250,247,0.78);">No application. No credit pull. A 20-minute conversation where we look at your Schedule C, your SAMS or NAMS credential, your practice structure, and your goal &mdash; then we tell you which loan program fits and roughly what the numbers look like. If we&rsquo;re not the right shop, we&rsquo;ll tell you that too.</p>
        <div class="final-cta-actions">
          <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/schedule-call" class="btn btn-on-dark-primary btn-large">Talk to Our Team</a>
          <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/yacht-professionals/" class="btn btn-on-dark-secondary btn-large">Back to the yacht professionals hub</a>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-xs); color: rgba(250,250,247,0.5); margin-top: var(--s-6);">Stairway Mortgage is a division of NEXA Mortgage LLC. Jim Blackburn NMLS #1072866.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


